&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Zabriskije&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;@Zabriskije&lt;/a&gt; - 修复幽灵滚动问题&lt;/li&gt;
